Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治療
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直繼 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管來啊 這史萊姆祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你在把我當盾牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你加血的啦 所以再為我獻身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副本區域中存在5-10只特殊怪物——RaidBoss
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(326,670)}RaidZone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一監獄的邦迪彌耶 怎麼看都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洛斯的九大監獄啊 真懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.20,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)\fs28}註：*在第十個資料片「夢幻的心臟」中實裝的團隊副本海洛斯的九大監獄 開始只能攻打第一~第八監獄 攻略順序自由 全部通關後可以開啟第九監獄 根據監獄的通關順序會影響後期副本的難度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那時候的RaidBoss吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:46.36,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(152,72)\fad(150,200)}布裡甘提亞第一庭院的邦迪彌耶 Lv.91
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:46.36,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(130,201)\fad(150,200)}Rank/Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物模型的重複使用還是挺常見的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位 它要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家散開 準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一隊攻擊右腳正面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二隊攻擊左腳側面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三隊到左後方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四隊右後方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擺好陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束縛吼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}AnchorhHowl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先按照通常套路去磨血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給輸出職業加上攻擊力增加和追加傷害的buff
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後衛則從安全範圍進行遠距離攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要給作為坦克的戰士提供大量回復
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和降低傷害或增加防禦力的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後最重要的是仇恨管理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說將敵人的注意力保持在坦克身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}這個大鳥怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想飛起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是某種攻擊的發動前兆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無視仇恨的範圍攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誠惠 損傷報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動阻礙5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石化4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即死1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點幫我回復
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清buff時沒有的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上DEBUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 迪米卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的回復誰等的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎嘯拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}TigerEchoFist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十字斬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}CrossSlash
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算打掉了十分之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那一波又有幾個人倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個跳到下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個從區域中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 向上面移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它會噴火的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAID BOSS的攻擊會隨著HP的減少會變得強力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放技能時機和屬性都和之前不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得下流了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想對付必須採取與通常的戰鬥不同的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直繼 特托拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是聚集強大的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法到達勝利的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特隆石化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 坦克全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有沒有治療
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有了 全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉 這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反覆進行滅團或撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索對手的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其突破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反覆進行了和第一庭院的邦迪彌耶的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒全滅過 但不斷忍受和那相差無幾的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又失誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓身體記住模式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行分析試了多種攻略方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團隊副本就是根據對像不同可進行一個月以上的長期戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(227,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是轉眼即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後會使用無視仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨機使十人狀態異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者使用讓人即死的那個技能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下次戰鬥時計算一下間隔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間隔是60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1003,710)}1 2 3 4…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞到背後去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上DEBUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快一點站好位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1003,710)}5 6 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAID BOSS的技能有冷卻時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能將其把握好 進行迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將傷害降到最小的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發光的技能沒放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好誒 把技能打斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣打掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加大DPS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將敵人的每個長處和短都記住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且穩定好團隊配合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就是時間的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將RAID BOSS打敗後可以獲得幻想級的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著是第二隻RAID BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖之庭院的愛爾萊茵達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是會狂刷清仇恨和召喚守護獸的難敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在十幾回的挑戰之後將其戰勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣將RAID BOSS一個個打敗 前往通關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是FULL RAID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從首殺副本開始後已經過了三星期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(501,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我去死怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了到下一回合之前等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米迪米的仇恨值…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少囉嗦祭不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米迪米後面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}WyvernKick
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治療流程都被打亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能進行援護了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越深入越能切實感受到這個副本的難易度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物的等級提升 被迫陷入苦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說攻略狀況了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連區域的全貌都沒抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不小心愛上我 那就對不起咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了趕緊點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 那麼我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回應大家的請求~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極光女神之治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}Aurora Heal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中火力攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避開近戰攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自打倒了最初的兩隻BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直沒能繼續碰到RaidBOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷宮的探索也止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥陷入了膠著狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為還有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指副本BOSS的數量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.68,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\an2\b1\fs35\pos(1037,63)}奈落的棧道 安全區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.68,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\pos(1007,169)}日本服務器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.68,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\pos(996,222)}緹雅斯頓山地地下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.68,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\pos(992,274)}副本/無怪物出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.68,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\pos(1077,388)}戰鬥行為可能區域\N全特技可以使用\N進入許可/無限制\N退出許可/無限制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三到四隻的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太樂觀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十天看來是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所面臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是補給的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反覆戰鬥會損耗裝備的耐久度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保持完備的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要擁有生產系技能的玩家對裝備進行修補
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉所帶的「神水晶之鏑箭」也有限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能讓一流的工匠用幻想級的素材來製造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,補給啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食物也是 不知道能撐到何時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑戰團隊副本需要與之相應的裝備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(484,670)}FullRaid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那些裝備 不挑戰副本的話也很難入手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(665,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,補修的素材也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他挑戰副本的公會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(660,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像會為了刷材料而專門去掃低等級副本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(956,670)}Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大災害之後我們來回刷副本也費了不少功夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(679,670)}RaidZone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們並沒有為了材料而去刷沒手感的本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可不是那種軟弱的公會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟咱們的會長可不會允許這種半吊子行為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我們如今才會跟他過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟隨著那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這裡也準備了一些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約能撐多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算上我這邊這些 大約也只能再撐20天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算不上有多少補助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記錄的地平線不是只有8人的弱小公會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼收集到那麼多的材料的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是一般人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕了圓桌會議的邀請之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處刷副本之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(659,670)}RaidZone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了薄野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不後悔自己所做過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然並不後悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一路我們很愉快哦 公會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要我們怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群軟弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連城惠的目的也沒有過問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就帶著大家來了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信著那樣的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道究竟什麼才算是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道究竟該對那些人說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我終究不過是個玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自出生以來 就不曾認真對待過遊戲以外的什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎麼想的呢 城惠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛伏在地下雖然對我們來說正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對方也不是能一直矇混過去的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪南暫且不提
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的城惠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓頭人和守護戰士暫且不說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(641,670)}Guardian
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都是受了你的支援在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是在背後偷偷給予指示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米庫拉斯先生是哪一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪利西斯先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是賦予術士的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(600,670)}Enchanter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.10,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\pos(1015,164)\frx354\fry4\frz3.782}賦予效果 {\fs28\c&HDFC79B&\bord2\blur3\3c&HDFC79B&}物理攻擊力增加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.10,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\frz4.917\pos(1037,278)\frx2\fry8}所屬工會/{\b1\fs28}布裡甘提亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用鋒刃術 來強化我的攻擊力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(497,670)}Keen Edge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又用精神震盪來封鎖敵人的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(521,670)}Mind Shock
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然會被那個混蛋救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爺竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給他的菜裡分了比較多的蔬菜這事兒暴露了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概不是這個吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不讓人省心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 至少不是個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 肉湯祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(415,710)}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美味呢 直繼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…城他啊 感覺好像有點麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然他一直都工作不斷 總是一副愁眉苦臉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他 意外地很享受這種事 又還去裝傻賣呆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真正痛苦的時候卻沒人能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 他現在真的是在苦惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看來需要一個偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得那可能會奏效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要給他看看內褲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又…又是曉的詛咒嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我覺得他不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 既然這麼痛苦 為啥還要來這種地洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了保護家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說物理上建築
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是家 不如說是工會？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城鎮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對人來說 家和飯是必需品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來的世界就是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在現在的這個世界來說 就該是工會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然需要一個歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說是「家」的家 也就是說是秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個城鎮不能變得幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡的許多工會也不會幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨之 在那些工會裡的人們也會變得無精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城他啊 只要是為了保護自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是城鎮 還是世界 都會與之為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸宿…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉原嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該和瑪莉艾通念話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 還沒到約定的時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 直繼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒什麼祭的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的完全什麼都沒有祭的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的聖誕節和落雪節不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(699,670)}snowfell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是大地人冬天會舉辦的祭典嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道城惠哥能不能在聖誕節前趕回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.46,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H646E6D&\fs28\3c&HE3EAE9&\pos(136,508)\frz59.09\frx350\fry16}分辨率\N不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這時候 在原來的世界也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小勝雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和 和家人以外的人過聖誕節什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說了 哥懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年 大家一起過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕老人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落雪節是大家交換禮物的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有聖誕老人發禮物才叫聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 坐在馴鹿上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 坐的是雪橇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物啊 會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要口傳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有記載著口傳的卷軸 我絕對想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口傳怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉 什麼時候在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是神秘的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 曉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作辛苦了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃點點心喝點茶吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 口傳是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近在街上流傳的很火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輩也聽到了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡要概括就是 特技的新階級
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是特技
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根據使用的人不同 威力也會不同的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為技能的階級不一樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就算是同樣的特技
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:20.42,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an2\pos(565,156)\fad(150,0)}絕命的一閃/AssassiNeith
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初傳 中傳 奧傳 秘傳 根據階級的上升
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力也會上升
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想提高到中傳 需要同職業冒險者做出的卷軸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想學習奧傳 需要用稀有素材做出的卷軸對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這兩個都很貴 但是都是可以交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 想學習秘傳就必須突破專職任務
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就必須要參加團隊副本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(801,670)}RAID
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團隊副本…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(623,670)}RAID
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的口傳 傳聞是比秘傳還高的階級
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只是傳聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際已經學習成功 並得到確認的 非常少的樣子喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠哥說過有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 城惠哥竟然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 說口傳是確實存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也好想學習到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界在遊戲時代並不存在的 特技的新階級「口傳」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有六天就是聖誕節了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕薄 且軟弱的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不是你們的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,555)}別太猖狂了 區區冒險者們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城惠不在的秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自煩惱的曉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼城惠將自己留下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.17,0:24:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼自己會如此弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 蕾妮希雅也陷入了想要放棄的消極之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為大地人和冒險者是永遠無法互相理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.17,0:24:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 出現裂紋的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇往直前吧 再一次
